documentation.text:
@dev Reveal the actual sender of a camouflaged transfer
 @param camouflageId The camouflage ID to reveal
@dev Pause all transfers
@dev Unpause all transfers
@dev Override _update to emit camouflaged Transfer events
@dev Override decimals to match USDT (6 decimals)
